title: Winter Cold
description: The turkey is cooking in the ovenAs the family gathers around the table to prayIt's Christmas day and all they can do is cry... A little mute boy receives nothing he wished for on Christmas Day, but after he receives a mysterious gift, his life has completely changed.inter Cold is a drama visual novel featuring:- A deep and heartbreaking storyline that touches many interesting themes and topics- Brilliant art style, backgrounds and sprites- Awesome background music
